PrecisAppointment of RONALD KANTER, of Toronto, Ontario, MARGARET WEIR, of Toronto, Ontario, DAVID CHAPLEY, of Thornhill, Ontario, and LOIS FIGG, of Toronto, Ontario, as full-time members of the Convention Refugee Determination Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Toronto Regional Office), to hold office during good behaviour for a term of two years, effective June 26, 2000.
